      "deeperQuestionText": "In a solar PV installation, why is an inverter necessary to make the system compatible with standard domestic appliances?",
      "deeperAnswerGuidance": [
        "Solar panels generate Direct Current (DC)",
        "Domestic appliances and the grid operate on Alternating Current (AC)",
        "The inverter performs the specific task of converting DC to AC",
        "Without it, the power type would be incompatible with the household wiring"
      ],
      "hint": "Recall the difference between a rectifier (AC to DC) and an inverter (DC to AC)."
    }
  ]
